{"title": "Drum", "summary": "Large Surface Luminaire", "body": "Bold, modern, and functional, Drum is a pendant and surface luminaire that provides a generous and wide spread of general lighting. The offset conical baffle adds a unique touch to this cylindrical fixture. Available in combinations of three diameters and three heights, this luminaire offers a wide variety of size and color configurations.\n\n*2020*\n[lp=DRUM SURFACE - C82 Trio Colors.jpg]\n\n**&&Process&&**\n\n[sp=Drum Process (1).jpg][sp=Drum Process (4).jpg][sp=Drum Process (2).jpg]\n\n**&&Final Product&&**\n\n[lp=Government of Canada Office (1).jpg]\n[lp=P82-scene.jpg]", "image": "DRUM SURFACE COVER.jpg", "id": 17}